# Design System SistemasEscolares

## Paleta — NUNCA usar colores literales fuera de la paleta

```
brand.jet      = #333333  → text-brand-jet, bg-brand-jet
brand.primary  = #40848D  → text-primary-*, bg-primary-*, border-primary-*
brand.secondary= #739FA5  → text-brand-secondary
brand.surface  = #C1D7DA  → bg-brand-surface, hover:bg-brand-surface/40
brand.white    = #FFFFFF  → bg-white, text-white
```

Semánticos: `success-*`, `warning-*`, `danger-*`, `info-*`.

**PROHIBIDO** usar `indigo-*`, `blue-*`, `red-*` directamente. Reemplazar siempre con la paleta SE.

## Componentes — SIEMPRE usar `<x-ui.*>`

| En vez de... | Usar |
|---|---|
| `<button class="bg-indigo-...">` | `<x-ui.button variant="primary">` |
| `<input class="border-gray-...">` | `<x-ui.input>` o `class="input"` |
| `<div class="rounded-lg shadow ring-...">` | `<x-ui.card>` |
| `<table class="min-w-full divide-...">` | `<x-ui.table>` + `<x-ui.th>` + `<x-ui.td>` |
| `<div class="bg-green-50...">` (alerta) | `<x-ui.alert variant="success">` |
| Toast manual | `$this->dispatch('toast', message: '...', type: 'success')` |

## Tipografía

Sistema UI stack: ya definido en `tailwind.config.js → fontFamily.sans`.
**No importar Google Fonts.** No añadir `@import url(fonts.googleapis.com...)`.

## Iconos

Usar exclusivamente Heroicons inline como componentes Blade:
```blade
<x-icons.plus class="w-4 h-4" />
<x-icons.pencil class="w-4 h-4 text-primary-500" />
```

No importar paquetes de iconos externos. Agregar nuevos iconos en `resources/views/components/icons/`.

## Sombras y radios estándar

```
Cards:   shadow-card + rounded-xl
Modales: shadow-modal + rounded-xl
Botones: rounded-lg
Badges:  rounded-full
```
